text: Honolulu is a 1939 American musical comedy movie directed by Edward Buzzell and starring Eleanor Powell, Robert Young, George Burns, Gracie Allen, Rita Johnson, Clarence Kolb. It was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer. == Other websites == * Category:1939 musical movies Category:1939 comedy movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Edward Buzzell
